  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613400/extras/cded50009e230e8d156bc23955dbd7b1.poster.avif?t=1745859138\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613400/extras/cded50009e230e8d156bc23955dbd7b1.webm?t=1745859138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613400/extras/cded50009e230e8d156bc23955dbd7b1.mp4?t=1745859138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613400/extras/b2cfc35f4081d375030b478cd25145a3.poster.avif?t=1745859138\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613400/extras/b2cfc35f4081d375030b478cd25145a3.webm?t=1745859138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613400/extras/b2cfc35f4081d375030b478cd25145a3.mp4?t=1745859138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Get behind the wheel in Taxi Rush and transport your passengers in this crazy big city! As a crazy taxi driver, get your passengers where they need to go on time. Traffic? Traffic Rules? Police? Red Lights? No, no, no, no, no, no. You're a crazy, lawless driver. Jump with your car if you have to!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🚖 Become a Taxi Driver</strong></h2> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Pick up customers and take them where they want to go on time.<br></li><li> Traffic rules? Ha ha, drive as you like.<br></li><li> Don't like your customer or they talk too much? Then throw them out of your car!<br></li><li> Use all your skills to earn tips.<br></li><li> Discover different customers. Maybe an alien?<br></li><li> Drive, explore the city and earn money.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613400/extras/00a37ed3e9eec92f31b1c38ff4f363e0.poster.avif?t=1745859138\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613400/extras/00a37ed3e9eec92f31b1c38ff4f363e0.webm?t=1745859138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613400/extras/00a37ed3e9eec92f31b1c38ff4f363e0.mp4?t=1745859138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🚖 Grow Your Business</strong></h2> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Build your own taxi empire!<br></li><li> Hire cabbies as crazy as you.<br></li><li> Modify your car however you want.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613400/extras/69549c0d4a5224fbcecaea740bf031ed.poster.avif?t=1745859138\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613400/extras/69549c0d4a5224fbcecaea740bf031ed.webm?t=1745859138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2613400/extras/69549c0d4a5224fbcecaea740bf031ed.mp4?t=1745859138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🚖 Different Cars & Different Stories</strong></h2> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Buy your new car and new character with the money you earn!<br></li><li> Each character and car has different features.<br></li><li> Get the best taxi car!</li></ul><br>Taxi Rush is not just a driving game, but an experience that combines speed, strategy and a story of personal achievement. Do you have what it takes to become the best taxi driver in town? Then, press the starter and go on an adventure!",
